title: S16 Ep67: Clairvoyage: Stories & Nightmares of Having Psychic Abilities
itunes:title: Clairvoyage: Stories & Nightmares of Having Psychic Abilities
description:
Darkness Radio presents Clairvoyage: Stories & Nightmares of Having Psychic Abilities with Stephanie Milanowski

Dave & Tim are joined by guest Stephanie Milanowski to discuss her new book and her life dealing with gifts that allow her to see, hear and communicate telepathically with ghosts, demons and otherworldly creatures.  Stephanie opens up about what it is like to grow up with these gifts and tells us some of the horror stories associated with being gifted.  

Get her book here: www.amazon.com/shop/darknessradiodave

Visit her site here: www.StephanieMilanowski.com

House Healing here: www.HouseHealing.com
